title: Person of Interest: Reese, Shaw & Fusco VS Mob
author: POI Fights
comment: This video has become  nostalgic for me. I believe that this was the last time that Reese,Fusco,Shaw,and Bear worked together as a well oiled machine .Soon after Shaw was lost.As we all know the team has not been the same since.
He runs out of ammo during every shoot out, wins every fire fight even when the enemy has assault rifles , never picks up their guns. doesn't use cover and doesn't wear a vest .
Since when did he Italian mob have blacks?
